<i>noun</i>: 소송인 [소송인] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>소송인 [소송인]</dt><br>
<dd>litigant</dd><br>
<dd>다툼이 일어났을 때 법률에 따라 판결해 달라고 법원에 요구한 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>The person who requested the court to make a formal decision according to the laws on a point of contention between people.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>